title: S4 Ep35: Does malnutrition cause disease?
itunes:title: Does malnutrition cause disease?
description: The records of London's Foundling Hospital provide centuries of information on children's health. Eric Schneider tells Tim Phillips how he used this data to discover surprising information about the link between nutrition and common childhood illnesses.
